   Kiel, Carrie A.; Porter, J. Mark; McDade, Lucinda A., Calif Bot Garden, 1500 North Coll Ave, Claremont, CA 91711 USA.
   Manzitto-Tripp, Erin, Univ Colorado, Museum Nat Hist, Boulder, CO 80309 USA.
   Manzitto-Tripp, Erin, Dept Ecol \& Evolutionary Biol, Boulder, CO 80309 USA.
   Fisher, Amanda E., Calif State Univ Long Beach, Dept Psychol, 1250 Bellflower Blvd, Long Beach, CA 90807 USA.},
